    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable, no-nonsense vehicle that gets you where you need to go? This car is in fair condition \u2014 it runs and drives reliably, making it a smart pick for everyday commuting or a budget-conscious buyer. It has some wear that comes with its age, but nothing that gets in the way of dependable daily use. If you're looking for honest transportation at a great value, this one deserves a look!",
      "price": 18500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
